T02TD2811E:166b-0: @166b * // thugs rje chen po lam gyi bzhi mdo can la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2811E:166b-1: rgyu dang mi rgyu'i 'jig rten la //

T02TD2811E:166b-3: lam gyi bzhi mdor kun don spyod //
T02TD2811E:166b-4: skyo ba med skyob sgrub thabs bri //
T02TD2811E:166b-5: byang chub sems dpa' chen po snying rje chen po can gyis bdag nyid grags pa la sogs pa'i phyir ma yin par lam gyi bzhi mdo dang tshod 'dus chen po la sogs par 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug bsgrub par bya'o //

T02TD2811E:167a-0: re zhig skye bo mang po'i spyod yul du byed pa'i gnas ni 'phags pa dgyes pa'i gnas yin pas der spyil bu 'am khang bu la sogs pa gnas mal kha dog dkar po padmo'i tog @167a * //

T02TD2811E:167a-3: skyob pa skyob pa med gcig pu //
T02TD2811E:167a-4: ljon shing bzang la sku brten te //
T02TD2811E:167a-6: bcu drug na tshod mdzes pa'o //
T02TD2811E:167a-7: cho ga bzang shes bdag dang lha //
